  "response": "The question of whether Kim Kardashian is the \"worst\" role model for women is subjective and can vary based on individual values, beliefs, and priorities. Some people admire her for her business acumen, entrepreneurship, and ability to navigate the entertainment industry. Others criticize her for promoting certain ideals related to beauty, lifestyle, and fame that they believe can be detrimental.\n\nIt's important to recognize that role models can be perceived differently based on personal experiences and societal norms. Some may find her approachable and relatable, while others may feel that her lifestyle sets unrealistic expectations. Ultimately, each person should evaluate role models based on their own criteria and decide who they admire or aspire to emulate.",
